rows.label: tlk42350143_05_msg0001
rows.name:
D-don't worry, mo! I-it's okay,
mo! If you just buy this product
from Kurolo, somehow—

rows.label: tlk42350143_05_msg0002
rows.name:
—it's not going to be okay, mo! Divine Beasts
are fighting each other, one product can't
possibly solve that! Don't be ridiculous, mo!

rows.label: tlk42350143_05_msg0003
rows.name:
Am I going to die without
accomplishing a single great
deed? I don't want that, mo~!
